{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequent pre-processing involved a series of indispensable transformations to homogenize the textual data.",
    "To ensure consistency, all text was converted to lowercase, aligning the text case for uniform analysis.",
    "Furthermore, several crucial cleansing steps were undertaken: the removal of Twitter handlers (mentions), extraction of hashtags, and elimination of URLs, ensuring the extraction of valuable content while removing elements that don't contribute substantively to our analysis.",
    "Employing regular expressions, special characters were meticulously removed, retaining only alphanumeric characters for meaningful analysis.",
    "To bolster the dataset's quality, a meticulous curation process was applied, removing single characters and consolidating multiple spaces into a singular space."
  ]
}